        "source": "github.readme"
      },
      "html": "<h1>CodeIgniter 3.0.3 base_url Fix</h1>\n\n<h2>How to</h2>\n<p>Download the <code>MY_Config.php</code> file and put it into the <code>application/core</code> folder of your CodeIgniter project.  </p>\n<h2>Important</h2>\n<p>If you&apos;ve set in your config file <code>application/congif/config.php</code> another value than &quot;<em>MY_</em>&quot; in the <code>$config[&apos;subclass_prefix&apos;]</code> option, change the name of <code>MY_Config.php</code> replacing &quot;<em>MY_</em>&quot; with your value.  </p>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<pre>$config[<span class=\"hljs-string\">&apos;subclass_prefix&apos;</span>] = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&apos;CUSTOM_&apos;</span>;\nMY_Config.php =&gt; CUSTOM_Config.php</pre>"
